Ing '''Segovia''' metung yang [[Provinces of Spain|lalawigan]] ning kalibudtran/pangulung [[Espanya]], king mauling dake ning [[Autonomous communities of Spain|autonomous communidad]] ning[[Castile-Leon|Castile ampong León]]. Ding kayang danggut ilapin deng [[Burgos (province)|Burgos]], [[Soria (province)|Soria]], [[Guadalajara (province)|Guadalajara]], [[Community of Madrid|Madrid]], [[Ávila (province)|Ávila]], ampong [[Valladolid (province)|Valladolid]].

Ing lalawigan atin populasiun a 149,286, nung nu 35% pakaatuknang la keng tungku, ing [[Segovia]]. Kareng 209 a balen ning lalawigan, maiggit kapitna kareng barriu kulang la keng 200 a katau deng pakatuknang.

Lawen ya ing [[Tala da reng balen king Segovia]].

